functions.label: KibanaStyledComponentsThemeProvider
description: A `styled-components` `ThemeProvider` that incorporates EUI dark mode.

functions.label: KibanaStyledComponentsThemeProviderDecorator
description:
Storybook decorator using the EUI theme provider. Uses the value from
`globals` provided by the Storybook theme switcher.

children.label: component
signature: React.ComponentProps<C> extends { theme?: T | undefined; } ? C : never

interfaces.label: EuiTheme
description: A `deprecated` structure representing a Kibana theme containing variables from the current EUI theme.
